This directory contains all configuration data which can be changed.
After the first installation this directory is almost emtpy.


First Installation:
-------------------
Copy the whole content of directory ../vdropt-sample into this directory, or
rename the directoy ../vdropt-sample to ../vdropt


Update an existing installation:
--------------------------------
The existing configuration data in this directory will not be changed.
After installing an update, the directory ../vdropt-sample contains all new configuration data.
You can copy necessary data into this directory. This is mostly needed if a new plugin exists or
other new configuration data has been deployed. Normally no further actions are necessary.
